short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Receives data from the ParLevel Serial Monitor application to fill in web forms with data received from money counters.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension works together with the ParLevel Serial Monitor Chrome App to automatically fill money inputs (Coins and Bills) that are transmitted by Cummins Allison counters into the ParLevel VMS Consolidation screen.
